        F(x|A,B,C,D,G) = D+(A-D)/Power(1+Power(x/C,B),G)    (5PL model)

    Here:
        * A, D - unconstrained
        * B>=0 for 4PL, unconstrained for 5PL
        * C>0
        * G>0 (if present)

